<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6499> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6499" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Commander of Cyrene under Antony. He refused to receive Antony after Actium, and in 30 brought the legions in Cyrene over to Octavian (Dio 51.5.6; cf. Plut. Ant. 69.2; Dio 51.9.1; Oros. 6.19.15; Grueber, CRRBM 2.583f., with the inscription Scarpus Imp.). See PIR 3.40, no. 311; De Laet no. 287." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6209> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6209" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Antony placed him in charge of supplies with one legion at Amphipolis while he advanced to Philippi (App. BC 4.107)." .
